      "review_summary": "Adds a default-off migrated gitcrawl cluster repair lane, gitcrawl-store DB lookup, lane-specific repair capacity config, docs, and regression tests.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the remaining review finding: source inspection at the PR head shows docs/limits.md says the repair hard cap comes from lane config while src/repair/limits.ts and src/limits.ts set it to workers.max. I did not run tests because this review must keep the checkout read-only.",
